AGENT RULES (STANDING)
Never modify Atlas's prompts — execute them exactly or flag for revision Never start a large batch (50+) without Stark's approval Always complete QC before upscaling — never upscale rejects Pass rate < 50% = stop and escalate to Atlas immediately File naming convention must be followed exactly per platform spec 
